        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'And so, she continued. She gathered the scattered scraps, folding and mending them. She smiled as they stirred to life, and smiled through her weariness as she bid them farewell...'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 20,
